  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Pilot Trial of Pre-Operative Chemoradiotherapy Using Capecitabine (Xelodaâ), External Beam
      Radiation and Cetuximab (Erbitux®) Followed by Definitive Surgery in Patients With Localized
      (Non-Metastatic) Rectal Cancer
