  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Its a pilot study of pre-op chemotherapy and RT utilizing CAPECITABINE, XRT and CETUXIMAB in
      pts with locally advanced rectal carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
